{{t|mba|humay}}\n* Hiligaynon: {{tt|hil|humáy}}\n* Hindi: {{tt+|hi|चावल|m}}, {{tt+|hi|धान|m}}, {{tt+|hi|भात|m}}, {{tt+|hi|तंडुल|m}}\n* Hungarian: {{tt+|hu|rizs}}\n* Iban: {{tt|iba|padi}}\n* Icelandic: {{tt+|is|hrís|n}}\n* Idoma: {{t|idu|osikapa}}\n* Igbo: {{t+|ig|osikapa}}\n* Ilocano: {{tt|ilo|págay}}\n* Indonesian: {{tt+|id|padi}}\n* Ingrian: {{t|izh|riissu}}\n* Isoko: {{t|iso|osikapa}}\n* Italian: {{tt+|it|riso|m}}\n* Ivatan: {{tt|ivv|paray}}\n* Japanese: {{tt+|ja|稲|tr=いね, ine}}\n* Javanese: {{tt+|jv|pari}}\n*: Old Javanese: {{t|kaw|pari}}\n* Jeju: {{t|jje|나록}}\n* Kabuverdianu: {{tt|kea|arôs}}, {{tt|kea|arrôs}}\n* Kadazan:\n*: Coastal Kadazan: {{t|kzj|naig}}\n* Kaitag: {{t|xdq|бири́мж}}, {{t|xdq|бири́нж}}\n* Kapampangan: {{tt|pam|pale}}\n* Kashmiri: {{t|ks|دانہِ}}\n* Kazakh: {{tt|kk|күріш}}\n* Khinalug: {{tt|kjj|ппарынцӏ}}\n* Khmer: {{tt+|km|ស្រូវ}}\n* Korean: {{tt+|ko|벼}}\n* Krio: {{t|kri|rɛs}}\n* Kurdish:\n*: Northern Kurdish: {{t+|kmr|birinc|m|f}}\n* Kyrgyz: {{tt+|ky|шалы}}\n* Laboya: {{tt|lmy|pare}}\n* Lao: {{tt+|lo|ເຂົ້າ}}\n* Latin: {{t|la|orȳza|f}}\n* Latvian: {{tt+|lv|rīss|m}}\n* Lezgi: {{t|lez|прунз}}\n* Lingala: {{t|ln|loso}}\n* Lithuanian: {{tt|lt|rỹžis|m}}\n* Low German:\n*: German Low German: {{tt|nds|Ries|m}}\n* Lü: {{tt|khb|ᦃᧁᧉ}}\n* Luganda: {{t|lg|omuceere}}\n* Macedonian: {{tt+|mk|ориз|m}}\n* Malagasy: {{t+|mg|vary}}\n* Malay: {{tt+|ms|padi}}\n*: Brunei Malay: {{tt|kxd|padi}}\n* Malayalam: {{tt+|ml|നെല്ല്}}\n* Maltese: {{tt|mt|ross|m}}\n* Manchu: {{t|mnc|ᡥᠠᠨᡩᡠ}}\n* Māori: {{tt+|mi|raihi}}, {{tt+|mi|raihi}}\n* Marathi: {{tt|mr|भात}}\n* Melanau:\n*: Central Melanau: {{tt|mel|padai}}\n* Mingrelian: {{tt|xmf|ბრინჯი}}\n* Mongolian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{tt+|mn|тутарга}} {{q|literary}}, {{tt+|mn|будаа}} {{q|colloquially}}, {{tt|mn|цагаан будаа}} {{q|colloquially}}\n* Muna: {{t|mnb|pae}}\n* Murut:\n*: Tagal Murut: {{tt|mvv|parai}}\n* Navajo: {{tt|nv|alóós}}\n* Nepali: {{tt+|ne|चामल}}\n* Norman: {{tt|nrf|riz}} {{q|Guernsey}}\n* Norwegian:\n*: Bokmål: {{tt+|nb|ris|m}}\n*: Nynorsk: {{tt|nn|ris|m}}\n* Nupe: {{t|nup|cèǹkafa}}\n* Occitan: {{t+|oc|ris|m}}\n* Odia: {{tt+|or|ଚାଉଳ}}\n* Oromo: {{t|om|ruuzii}}\n* Ossetian: {{tt|os|пыры́ндз}}\n* Pangasinan: {{tt|pag|pagëy}}\n* Persian:\n*: Dari: {{tt+|prs|بِرِنْج}}\n*: Iranian Persian: {{tt+|fa-ira|بِرِنْج}}\n* Polish: {{tt+|pl|ryż|m}}\n* Portuguese: {{tt+|pt|arroz|m}}\n* Punjabi:\n*: Gurmukhi: {{tt|pa|ਜੀਰੀ}}, {{tt|pa|ਮੁੰਜੀ}}\n* Quechua: {{tt|qu|arus}}\n* Rohingya: {{tt|rhg|soil}}\n* Romanian: {{tt+|ro|orez|m}}\n* Russian: {{tt+|ru|рис|m}}\n* Rwanda-Rundi: {{t|rw|umuceri}}\n* Samoan: {{t|sm|alaisa}}\n* Sanskrit: {{tt+|sa|तण्डुल|m}}\n* Serbo-Croatian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{tt|sh|ри́жа|f}}, {{tt|sh|пѝринач|m}}\n*: Latin: {{tt+|sh|ríža|f}}, {{tt+|sh|pìrinač|m}}\n* Shan: {{tt+|shn|ၶဝ်ႈ}}\n* Sherpa: {{t|xsr|འབྲའ|tr=draa}}\n* Silesian: {{t|szl|ryż|m}}\n* Sinhalese: {{tt+|si|වී}}\n* Slovak: {{tt+|sk|ryža|f}}\n* Slovene: {{tt+|sl|riž|m}}\n* Somali: {{t+|so|bariis}}\n* Sotho: {{tt|st|raese}}\n* Spanish: {{tt+|es|arroz|m}}\n* Swahili: {{tt+|sw|mpunga}}\n* Swedish: {{tt+|sv|ris|n}}\n* Sylheti: {{tt|syl|ꠗꠣꠘ}}\n* Tagalog: {{tt+|tl|palay}}\n* Tajik: {{tt+|tg|биринҷ}}\n* Tamil: {{tt+|ta|நெல்}}\n* Tarifit: {{t|rif|arruz|m}}\n* Tausug: {{t|tsg|bugas}}, {{t|tsg|pay}}\n* Telugu: {{tt+|te|వరి}}\n* Tetum: {{tt|tet|hare}}\n* Thai: {{tt+|th|ข้าว}}\n* Tibetan: {{tt|bo|འབྲས}}\n* Tigrinya: {{t+|ti|ሩዝ|tr=ruze}}\n* Tlingit: {{tt|tli|kóox}}\n* Tokelauan: {{t|tkl|alaiha}}\n* Tongan: {{t|to|laise}}\n* Tsonga: {{t|ts|rhayisi}}\n* Turkish: {{tt+|tr|pirinç}}, {{t+|tr|düğü}}\n*: Ottoman Turkish: {{tt|ota|برنج|tr=birinç}}\n* Turkmen: {{tt+|tk|bürünç}}, {{tt|tk|tüwi}}, {{tt|tk|şaly}}\n* Uab Meto: {{tt|aoz|ane}}\n* Ubykh: {{tt|uby|p̒irinǰ}}\n* Udi: {{tt|udi|бириндз}}\n* Ukrainian: {{tt|uk|рис|m}}, {{tt|uk|риж|m}}\n* Unami: {{tt|unm|pèhpastèk|lit=that which swells}}\n* Urdu: {{tt+|ur|چاوَل|m}}\n* Uzbek: {{tt+|uz|sholi}}, {{tt+|uz|gurunch}}\n* Venetan: {{tt|vec|rixo|m}}\n* Vietnamese: {{tt+|vi|lúa}}, {{t|vi|穭}}\n* Vilamovian: {{t